**Bella Cucina — Paid Media Performance Analytics**
Tool: Advanced Microsoft Excel
Period: Q1 2026 (January – March)

**Overview**
End-to-end paid media analytics project consolidating ad performance data from TikTok, Google Ads, Facebook, and Instagram into a single Excel workbook. 
The analysis covers campaign measurement, platform comparison, funnel analysis, and weekly trend tracking — structured as a real client deliverable.

**Business Questions Answered**
Which platform delivered the best return on ad spend?
Which campaign was most cost-efficient and should be repeated?
Where should budget be reallocated next quarter?

**Workbook Structure**
12-tab Excel workbook covering the full analytics workflow:
Raw Data — separate tabs for each platform (TikTok, Google Ads, Facebook, Instagram)
Combined Data — all 4 platforms unified into one table (2,437 rows)
Platform Summary — KPIs, pivot table, and charts by platform
Campaign Analysis — performance breakdown by campaign
Monthly Trends — January vs February vs March comparison
Funnel Analysis — Impression → Click → Conversion by platform
Trend Analysis — weekly performance heatmap + seasonal cohort comparison
Platform KPIs — dynamic XLOOKUP tool with dropdown selector
Client Dashboard — one-page executive summary

**Advanced Excel Features**

Pivot Tables
XLOOKUP with dropdown data validation
Calculated KPIs — CTR%, CPC, CPA, Conv Rate%, CPM
Conditional Formatting heatmaps
Combo Charts (bar + line)
Funnel visualization using shapes
Power Query for data consolidation
Named Tables for dynamic references

**Skills Demonstrated**
Advanced Excel,Pivot Tables, XLOOKUP, Power Query, Paid Media Analytics,Campaign Measurement, Multi-Platform Reporting, Data Visualization, 
Funnel Analysis Client Reporting
